heading: 2. The 16th day of December 2020 is fixed as the day on which section 218,
text_raw:
2. The 16th day of December 2020 is fixed as the day on which section 218, 
in so far as it is not already in operation, of the Legal Services Regulation Act 
2015 (No. 65 of 2015) shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

10 December, 2020. 

HELEN MCENTEE, 
Minister for Justice. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 18th December, 2020. 

 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 [604] 3

EXPLANATORY NOTE 

(This note is not part of the Instrument and does not purport to be a legal 
interpretation.) 

This Order fixes 16 December 2020 as the day on which section 218, in so far 
as it is not already in operation, of the Legal Services Regulation Act 2015 (No. 
65 of 2015) comes into operation.
